    "| `delay_rate = arr_del15 / arr_flights` | ✅ Normalised, comparable across airports, range [0,1] |\n",
    "\n",
    "> **Definition:** `delay_rate` = proportion of arriving flights that were delayed ≥ 15 minutes."
